Citation.sTitle: Densities, Viscosities, Surface Tensions, and Speeds of Sound of Aqueous Solutions of Piperidine + Pyrrolidine + Water
Citation.sAbstract: In the present paper, density, viscosity, speeds of sound, and surface tension have been determined for piperidine + pyrrolidine + water ternary aqueous solutions at 20 deg C. The experimental results have been correlated with a Redlich-Kister type equation.
